com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims
Class IDTokenClaims

java.lang.Object
  com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims.JSONObjectClaims
      com.nimbusds.openid.connect.claims.IDTokenClaims

public class IDTokenClaims
extends JSONObjectClaims

ID Token claims, serialisable to a JSON object.

Example ID Token claims set: 

 {
   "iss"     : "http://server.example.com",
   "user_id" : "248289761001",
   "aud"     : "s6BhdRkqt3",
   "nonce"   : "n-0S6_WzA2Mj",
   "exp"     : 1311281970,
   "iat"     : 1311280970
 }

See http://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-messages-1_0.html#id_token

Version:
0.9 (2012-05-16)
Author:
Vladimir Dzhuvinov
